msgid ""
"For now, they bump and slide against one another when their paths cross. "
"We'll address this in the next part."
msgstr ""
"Por ahora, chocan y se deslizan entre sí cuando sus rutas se cruzan. "
"Abordaremos esto en la próxima parte."

